StmtSimple.StatementText: SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[LastEdited], [c].[Name15] FROM [Customers] AS [c] INNER JOIN [Profiles] AS [p] ON [c].[ProfileId] = [p].[Id] WHERE [p].[Id] IN ( SELECT [b].[value] FROM OPENJSON(@__biggestLicenses_0) WITH ([value] int '$') AS [b] ) ORDER BY [c].[LastEdited] DESC OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
